   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Educate &amp; empower youth&apos;s voice through film</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ICiT is an innovative endeavor that educates and empowers underserved youth through extraordinary filmmaking opportunities. ICiT youth go through a month long screenwriting camp, to learn and be mentored on how to write a great script. One script is selected and given to a professional producer and director, and turned into a world-class film, and premiered at the Nashville Film Festival, where these ICiT youth are celebrated and their stories are validated on the local and international stage.</narrative>
  </description>
